@node Printing and Reading
@chapter Printing and Reading

This chapter covers the printed representations of FSet collections, and two slightly different sets
of reader macros that allow collection expressions to be written in a similar notation in your
source code.

This table summarizes the printed representations of the persistent FSet types.

@anchor{Print syntax table}
@multitable @columnfractions .15 .75 .1
